# cqed-rhf

CQED-RHF mean-field energy and analytic nuclear gradients for the Pauli–Fierz Hamiltonian,
implemented on top of Psi4.

## Requirements

- Python >= 3.9
- Psi4 (via conda or system install)
- NumPy
- opt-einsum

## Installation

```bash
pip install cqed-rhf

